node.text: Okay guys I have always believed transparency is the best way to go. So here goes...I was honestly equally upset about the launch of @jolieandjace because I want the line to be affordable AND quality. Our first run we had someone hand sewing which made the prices way higher.  We have been able to switch manufacturers due to high demand therefore lower costs AND SAME GREAT QUALITY!  so tomorrow we launch the new prices. $30 off on the cozy set!! In the new year I will be making more pieces and will find other materials to create even lower cost pieces so everyone is happy because I want us all to be cozy. ALSO. We have been able to size up to size 18. I will work very hard to continue to be more inclusive in sizes in the new year. I want us to all be cozy and happy. SHOP TOMORROW AT 9am PACIFIC!!!! I’m excited to grow this line with more styles and cozy in 2021 with y’all!  P.s. for the people that bought the first round, check your inbox in the next few days...got something for you;)

node.text: That’s a wrap😭😭😭. I am absolutely terrible with goodbyes and this movie has by far been the hardest to say goodbye to.  It came at such a perfect time in my life and I feel so blessed to have had this experience with the people I shared set with.  The cast…The crew…The town…all of it was 🙌🏼. I can’t WAIT for y’all to watch this movie this Christmas season on @lifetimetv !!! Until next time…. #itsawonderfullifetime

Hands down the best set visits with them ever. I hope they never forget the memories we made here because they will forever fill my heart.  Gigi @gigipowersss my lil sis, we love you so much. I can’t thank you enough for everything the last 2 weeks.  Gigi go crush college and kids I’ll see you in a week !!!!
